remarks: Two equivalent expressions for double existential uniqueness. (Contributed by NM, 2-Feb-2005.)  (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 17-Oct-2016.)  (Proof shortened by Wolf Lammen, 2-Oct-2019.)
statement:
2eu6 $p |- ( ( E! x E. y ph /\ E! y E. x ph ) <-> E. z E. w A. x A. y ( ph <-> ( x = z /\ y = w ) ) ) $.
$d ph w z $.
$d w x y z $.
